{
  "title": "KV Cache Compression, But What Must We Give in Return? A Comprehensive Benchmark of Long Context Capable Approaches",
  "authors": [
    "Jiayi Yuan",
    "Hongyi Liu",
    "Shaochen (Henry) Zhong",
    "Yu-Neng Chuang",
    "Songchen Li",
    "Guanchu Wang",
    "Duy Le",
    "Hongye Jin",
    "Vipin Chaudhary",
    "Zhaozhuo Xu",
    "Zirui Liu",
    "Xia Hu"
  ],
  "abstract": "Long context capability is a crucial competency for large language models (LLMs) as it mitigates the human struggle to digest long-form texts. This capability enables complex task-solving scenarios such as book summarization, code assistance, and many more tasks that are traditionally manpower-intensive. However, transformer-based LLMs face significant challenges with long context input due to the growing size of the KV cache and the intrinsic complexity of attending to extended inputs; where multiple schools of efficiency-driven approaches — such as KV cache quantization, token dropping, prompt compression, linear-time sequence models, and hybrid architectures — have been proposed to produce efficient yet long context-capable models. Despite these advancements, no existing work has comprehensively benchmarked these methods in a reasonably aligned environment. In this work, we fill this gap by providing a taxonomy of current methods and evaluating 10+ state-of-the-art approaches across seven categories of long context tasks. Our work reveals numerous previously unknown phenomena and offers insights — as well as a friendly workbench — for the future development of long context-capable LLMs.",
  "summary": "本研究针对大语言模型（LLM）的长上下文处理能力，系统性地评估了多种效率驱动的KV缓存压缩方法。研究问题为：不同的长上下文处理方法在各种长上下文任务中表现如何？核心方法包括：对10余种最新方法（涵盖KV缓存量化、令牌丢弃、提示压缩、线性时间序列模型及混合架构）进行归类，并在7类长上下文任务（单文档问答、多文档问答、摘要、少样本学习、合成任务、代码补全、大海捞针测试）上，基于Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct和Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2等模型进行基准测试。主要结果为：量化方法（如KIVI）在保持较高压缩比时性能损失最小；令牌丢弃方法中，H2O在预填充后丢弃令牌的策略优于预填充中丢弃；纯线性时间序列模型（如Mamba）在检索类任务上表现不佳；提示压缩方法（如LLMLingua2）在高压缩比下性能急剧下降。研究还发现，保持预填充过程不压缩对维持性能至关重要。",
  "keywords": [
    "KV cache compression",
    "long context",
    "large language models",
    "benchmark",
    "quantization",
    "token dropping",
    "prompt compression",
    "linear-time sequence models",
    "efficiency"
  ],
  "contributions": [
    "提供了涵盖10余种长上下文高效方法的全面基准测试，覆盖65种不同设置和7类长上下文任务。",
    "揭示了多个此前未知的现象，例如保持预填充过程不压缩对性能维持至关重要。",
    "开源了最小化、可复现且可扩展的基准测试平台，便于未来研究。",
    "基于实验结果，为长上下文LLM的未来发展提供了可操作的见解。"
  ],
  "limitations": [
    "由于不同方法的设计原理差异巨大（如量化方法与无KV缓存方法），无法实现所有方法的全局公平对齐。",
    "不同骨干模型（如Llama-3与Mamba）的预训练数据和质量不同，导致比较结果可能受预训练差异影响。",
    "部分方法（如线性注意力、KV缓存合并）因缺乏可用的开源大规模模型而未被纳入基准测试。",
    "基准测试仅覆盖了有限的模型和方法，并非详尽无遗。"
  ],
